Dialog e: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll come up with a plan for you.
Dialo ue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good?
Dialog e: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:28.58,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\3a&H32&\bord1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(424,473)}What about all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are your feelings of guilt gone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Kushieda-senpai is acting weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's a weird person by nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's been spacing out a lot more than usual recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.68,0:00:45.48,Episode Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.25\fad(300,400)\pos(670.909091,447)}Mercury Retrogrades\N at Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the big year-end sale is coming up soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then spring cleaning is after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the deepest parts of the cupboards to the tatami mats,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean every inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking of the wrong side; it's Christmas. Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have to be good for the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he's probably near the skies of Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa! Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that, I'll help you carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be great if he visits our house again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}love{\i0} Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you love Christmas, but why so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need a reason to love Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The street decorations are sparkling beautifully,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone is smiling and happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you'll spoil your dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, that's why I'm only eating one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to celebrate the end of your suspension tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, yellowtails are a natural product, so they're really expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least pretend to appreciate them because of the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay... Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yellowtail hotpot...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of yellowtails, yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During my suspension, did you get closer to Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No progress at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what did you do with the chance I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it couldn't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not here, Kushieda won't come to the meeting place in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she'll eat lunch with some other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then after school, she's busy with club{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"With all that waiting, do you think you're the faithful dog Hachiko?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you really think Minorin will come for you if you wait long enough?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fool. Stupid. Dumb dog. Idiot Ryuuji."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I was planning to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already said it all out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess not progressing at all is something that can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll come up with a plan for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas, so I'll be reborn as an angel of love to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you want, I'm a living saint right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint? I thought you were an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, I meant angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to give everyone a happy and joyful Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to take off one or two pieces of clothing, or even take it all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do I look like an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the crumbs are falling onto your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Get them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-san is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-san is back at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-san, we appreciate your effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We became your fans after we saw that fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle between the boss and the Palmtop Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was actually your victory, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought the first and final battle against her for your love...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you found out she's going to study abroad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fight was very difficult and caused a lot of hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the last person standing was the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the true victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My tense thigh and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my shaking calf...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.99,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, I'm back at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop singing weird songs and give me a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! I am a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, I missed you a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wait for us at the meeting place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I overslept so I had to rush here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my thighs are so sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how did I get here before you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were surrounded by some weird guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kushieda{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did I make a bad joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,`Morning, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Taiga, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda broke down again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up so badly. I should seriously become a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me be bald for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a high school girl like you wearing a bald wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Aisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kitamura-kun, good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.90,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, good morning to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.82,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning, that's why I'm saying "good morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean your pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,full of admiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am full of admiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings for Aisaka cannot be shown by just kneeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's why I'm lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of who it's for, you shouldn't fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot forgive someone, you have to talk to me about it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah, I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he's an assistant professor, but I saw him coming out of a casino!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that confirms it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't late for the date because of his work, but because he was playing slot machines!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.15,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(707,258)\frx15\frz337}Broadcasting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so I messaged one of my girlfriends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her what I should do, because I was being treated badly by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I found out something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such breathtaking development...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like there's no such occupation as an "assistant professor."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only something called an "assistant teacher."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was lying about his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, I haven't heard a thing from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to make our teacher cry, Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pretend we don't know it's actually Yuri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Cheering For Your Love" was brought to you by Kitamura Yuusaku, the God of Broken Hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Our guest today goes by the pseudonym of Y-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God of Broken Hearts? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, because of that confession, Kitamura has become the school's love saint{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he became a religious figure for those wanting to confess to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Kitamura will take all the bad luck away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something like "The Lucky God of Broken Hearts Legend."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Let me remind you, final exams are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do the people of our school love to believe legends so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Everyone, are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}I, the God of Broken Hearts, should also start studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this broadcast is really annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he bring up the topic of studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}but not everything goes my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't the title be "Cheering For Your Love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga is listening to it, so shut up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else she won't be able to hear the touching stories of Master Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, are you all right? You can hear it clearly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Taiga is being really modest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she would've killed Haruta had he done that any other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct, I'm being good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm being good because it's nearly Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look, Santa is watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you think Santa really exists. That's not like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid chi-, it's nearly Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're naughty, Santa won't visit your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely something strange about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen during your suspension?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is this a sign of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to die tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I going to die tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Thank you for listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the dreaded exams, it'll be Christmas, the time that everyone's looking forward to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now an announcement from the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the ceremony on Christmas Eve, there will be a Christmas party in the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come as couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Troubled by love? Can't ask him or her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try to invite the person you have feelings for to the party on that romantic night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.04,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:31.63,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}have{\i0} to invite Minorin to the Christmas Eve party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "Huh?" me! You have to confess to her in a snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're asking for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the holy Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the angel of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the holy child of Christmas and the model for being good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Santa is looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make your love life successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become Cupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like Cupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:28.77,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(640,248)}Good looking guys only
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My gosh, aren't you slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The special party for good looking guys is in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh! Look, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy over there is really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine with that type of guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, what a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of time left, so if you're hungry, eat this first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really that boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas and I'm waiting for you to do hot things to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, let's do hot things together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Someone cuter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want a cuter and prettier Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pervert. You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, Haruta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I the most unfortunate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about the real party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we have to decide who will be the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you love Christmas, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If everyone's asking me to go for it, I guess I'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come join me, you sugary-slug-dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what type of dog did you say I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, come join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not in the mood to go to a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's not the time for me to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up in an unbelievable way during the softball match,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we lost because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go and have fun at a party during a time like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the club members will look up to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have to practice for a match I have after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't need to help out, just come for the party and{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be going to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll help you guys set stuff up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan, you're going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll heat it up using the power of Class 2-C!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make this clear, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in your best interest to be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sort of plan is my specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll determine whether the party will be a success or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's also up to me to get {\i1}that{\i0} unhappy somebody to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, we'd be glad to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ryuu-chan, you're going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-chan is going too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, to study for our finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're meeting Kitamura and the others at the restaurant we always go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a salmon fillet in the frying pan. Remember to heat it up before you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'll be giza lonely gansu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with that "giza" and "gansu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a popular saying right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some new person at work told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young people say things like "gansu",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and "giza" sounds cute, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am giza-ly smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.53,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds really wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it sound wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is giza-ly good! It's tera-ly correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.04,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan, take care of Yasuko for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.50,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a rebellious reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:26.05,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Inko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your cute and honest side?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the book you borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.33,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\fs45\pos(640,278)\c&H76D0F1&\3c&HA7D2C9&\fad(0,300)}How to Cook A \NSpecial Poultry Christmas Meal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.33,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs45\pos(640,278)\c&H76D0F1&\3c&H6CA99D&\fad(0,300)}How to Cook A \NSpecial Poultry Christmas Meal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Inko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never cook you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. It's safe in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prize I got at the Cultural Festival for winning the Mr. Lucky Guy contest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call it "The Boss's Notes."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be nothing to be afraid of if we use this to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to be honest, this belongs to Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She let me win with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she can't come because of her job, so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit living in the past like an old person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not living in the{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to study at the place where Minorin works,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you should try and have a chat with her before everyone arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda took the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're ready to order, press the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Minorin is avoiding you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why would she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't speak to each other at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was the one who invited her to the study session.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you told me to leave everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys even talk to each other at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Going to work" was an excuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she said she's not going to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's feeling down because she screwed up during a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it your specialty to make everything better in times like these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how to support her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship with Minorin seems different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you guys were more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Takasu and Taiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing a winter coat on cold days makes you really warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo, you should buy one for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? This isn't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want a copy of The Boss's Notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't study by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this table is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta, go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara, you're sitting next to Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sit next to Haruta, and Kitamura, you're sitting at the other table.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I want to sit there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls should sit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right Taiga? Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not want to sit next to Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's order now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's going to the drink bar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No point in everyone getting up for drinks, so I'll get them for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want something hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, go to the drink bar with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you pairing Taiga and Kitamura up on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we've been found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I want you to help out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kitamura and Taiga would make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Kitamura is probably still upset about the Boss rejecting him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think a new love would help cure him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga likes Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you've noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprised, right? I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're the closest one to her since you take care of her and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so being surprised is only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, it seems like you really like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga likes Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known that for a long time, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.25,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it would be good for Taiga and Maruo to go out with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it'd be too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! You agree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though everyone says it, it's not like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "everyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Taiga goes out with Maruo, you don't think it'll be interesting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says you're gentle and you love to care for others,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.24,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you actually like Taiga, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll support you, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you like Kitamu{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying! I said I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is confusing. Guns and Roses...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:35.07,Ep Titles 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(323.636364,204)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:35.07,Ep Titles 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs69\pos(821.818182,546)}Beneath the Fir Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely be interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get your spirits up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have to come to the party, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be my usual self anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
